STREAMING_CHUNK:Configuring environment variables

Discord Bot Token (Get this from Discord Developer Portal)

DISCORD_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here

Discord Application Client ID

CLIENT_ID=your_application_client_id_here

Port for the Webhook Express Server (Railway handles this automatically, but good for local testing)

PORT=3000

Affiliate ID to be appended to product URLs (e.g., ?ref=my_code)

AFFILIATE_ID=your_affiliate_code_here

Secret key to authenticate incoming webhooks from your website

WEBHOOK_SECRET=a_secure_random_string_for_auth
